                    "content": {
                      "coreExplanation": "\n    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">\n        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(1)</h4>\n        <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\n                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">执业药师的配备要求</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\n                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>\n                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">\n                    \n    <p><strong>执业药师的配备要求</strong></p>\n    <p>该知识点需要重点掌握。在实际工作中，药师需要准确理解和应用相关知识，为患者提供专业的药学服务。</p>\n    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">\n        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(2)</h4>\n        <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\n                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">执业药师业务规范</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\n                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>\n                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">\n                    \n    <p><strong>执业药师业务规范</strong></p>\n    <p>该知识点需要重点掌握。在实际工作中，药师需要准确理解和应用相关知识，为患者提供专业的药学服务。</p>\n    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">\n        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(3)</h4>\n        <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\n                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">执业药师职业道德准则</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\n                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>\n                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">\n                    \n    <p><strong>执业药师职业道德准则</strong></p>\n    <p>该知识点需要重点掌握。在实际工作中，药师需要准确理解和应用相关知识，为患者提供专业的药学服务。</p>\n    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500\">\n        <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3\">(4)</h4>\n        <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\n                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">知识点说明</h5>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">药品零售企业执业药师药学服务指南</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200\">\n                <h5 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">详细内容</h5>\n                <div class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2\">\n                    \n    <p><strong>药品零售企业执业药师药学服务指南</strong></p>\n    <p>该知识点需要重点掌握。在实际工作中，药师需要准确理解和应用相关知识，为患者提供专业的药学服务。</p>\n    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    "
                    }
